Resource Profile: CDM Explanation of Benefit for Analytics

Official URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/cdm-explanation-of-benefit-for-analytics Version: 7.0.0
Active as of 2022-09-01 Computable Name: CDMExplanationOfBenefitForAnalytics

The CDMExplanationOfBenefitForAnalytics profile extends the base CDMExplanationOfBenefit profile with additional details that are useful for analytics.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: ExplanationOfBenefit/CDMExplanationOfBenefitForAnalyticsDrugInstance

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
